query:
SELECT r.recordId, COUNT(*) as cnt, MIN(r.id) as first_id, MAX(r.id) as last_id
FROM ridingRecords r
INNER JOIN users u ON r.userId = u.id
WHERE u.name = '로버'
GROUP BY r.recordId
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY cnt DESC;
